functionDecorators.name: getHistoricalPrice
functionDecorators.description: Returns historical price for a round id. roundId is NOT incremental. Not all roundIds are valid. You must know a valid roundId before consuming historical data. * ROUNDID VALUES: InValid: 18446744073709562300 Valid: 18446744073709562301. A timestamp with zero value means the round is not complete and should not be used.
